<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="A layout example that shows off a responsive product landing page.">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/blood-drop-icon.png" />
    <title>BloodBank.com &ndash; Homepage</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://yui.yahooapis.com/pure/0.6.0/pure-min.css">
    <!--[if lte IE 8]>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://yui.yahooapis.com/pure/0.6.0/grids-responsive-old-ie-min.css">
    <![endif]-->
    <!--[if gt IE 8]><!-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://yui.yahooapis.com/pure/0.6.0/grids-responsive-min.css">
    <!--<![endif]-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.0.3/css/font-awesome.css">
    <!--[if lte IE 8]>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/marketing-old-ie.css">
    <![endif]-->
    <!--[if gt IE 8]><!-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/marketing.css">
    <!--<![endif]-->
    <style>
        .indexBG
        {
            background-color:#303F9F;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header">
    <div class="home-menu pure-menu pure-menu-horizontal pure-menu-fixed">
        <a class="pure-menu-heading" href="/loggedinhomepage">BloodBank.com</a>
        <ul class="pure-menu-list">
            <li class="pure-menu-item pure-menu-selected"><a href="/loggedinhomepage" class="pure-menu-link">Home</a></li>
            <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="/logout" class="pure-menu-link">Logout</a></li>
            <li class="pure-menu-item"><%=user.local.email%></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="splash-container indexBG">
    <div class="splash">
        <h1 class="splash-head">Blood Bank</h1>
        <p class="splash-subhead">
            "Tears of a mother cannot save her Child. But your Blood can."
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="/donateblood/<%=user.local.email%>" class="pure-button pure-button-primary">Donate Blood</a>
            <a href="/requestblood/<%=user.local.email%>" class="pure-button pure-button-primary">Need Blood</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="content-head is-center">Why to Donate your blood?</h2>
        <div class="pure-g">
            <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    <i class="fa fa-rocket"></i>
                    “You’re somebody’s type"
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Blood being crucial to human is parted into some types.With their own combination requirement may or may not match.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    <i class="fa fa-mobile"></i>
                    You'r few moments-Someone's Life
                </h3>
                <p>
                    We spend time in enjoying and having fun. Some part of ur time of time may help in saving some innocent LIFE.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    <i class="fa fa-th-large"></i>
                    You give 1-We give 3
                </h3>
                <p>
                    We strive to replicate blood cells and create new cells.This is how we use ur precious blood more perfectly and avail to any.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    <i class="fa fa-check-square-o"></i>
                    More Need-Less avail
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Currently there is a huge requirement for blood but non availability makes someone's loose LIFE.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ribbon l-box-lrg pure-g">
        <div class="l-box-lrg is-center pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-2-5">
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" alt="File Icons" width="300" src="/images/7.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-3-5">
            <h2 class="content-head content-head-ribbon">What is BLOOD?</h2>
            <p>
                It's not made in a kitchen, but blood has ingredients, just like a recipe. To make blood, your body needs to mix:<br>
                <b>Red</b> blood cells, which carry oxygen throughout the body<br>
                <b>White</b> blood cells, which fight infections<br>
                <b>Platelets</b>, which are cells that help you stop bleeding if you get a cut<br>
                <b>Plasma</b>, a yellowish liquid that carries nutrients, hormones, and proteins throughout the body.<br>
                It is vital part of human body without which human cannot exit or live.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="content-head is-center">Blood Bank Information</h2>
        <div class="pure-g">
            <div class="l-box-lrg pure-u-1 pure-u-md-3-5">
                <h4>Contact Us</h4>
                <p>
                    E-Mail:info@bloodbank.in<br />
                    Phone:040-2424242<br />
                    Address:Blood Bank<br />
                    Hyderabad <br/>
                </p>
                <h4>Others</h4>
                <p>
                    We accept All the Requests 24X7.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer l-box is-center">
        Copyrights Reserved © BloodBank.com.
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>